## Endpoint Patterns

### GCNV REST API - CCFE Endpoint (Standard)

**Available Environments:**
- **Production**: `https://netapp.googleapis.com/v1/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/locations/{REGION}/{RESOURCE}`
- **Autopush**: `https://autopush-netapp.sandbox.googleapis.com/v1/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/locations/{REGION}/{RESOURCE}`
- **Staging**: `https://staging-netapp.sandbox.googleapis.com/v1/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/locations/{REGION}/{RESOURCE}`

GCNV Resources: `storagePools`, `volumes`, `snapshots`, `backups`, `backupVaults`, `backupPolicies`, `activeDirectories`, `kmsConfigs`, `replications`

### GCNV REST API - Proxy Endpoint
```
https://ncv.us-c1.autopush-tst.internal.npd.gnf.netapp.com/v1beta/projects/{PROJECT_NUMBER}/locations/{REGION}/{RESOURCE}
```

### ONTAP Expert Mode - CCFE Endpoint

**Available Environments:**
- **Production**: `https://netapp.googleapis.com/v1beta1/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/locations/{ZONE}/storagePools/{POOL_NAME}/ontap/api/{ONTAP_RESOURCE}`
- **Autopush**: `https://autopush-netapp.sandbox.googleapis.com/v1beta1/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/locations/{ZONE}/storagePools/{POOL_NAME}/ontap/api/{ONTAP_RESOURCE}`
- **Staging**: `https://staging-netapp.sandbox.googleapis.com/v1beta1/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/locations/{ZONE}/storagePools/{POOL_NAME}/ontap/api/{ONTAP_RESOURCE}`

### ONTAP Expert Mode - Proxy Endpoint
```
https://ncv.us-c1.autopush-tst.internal.npd.gnf.netapp.com/v1beta/projects/{PROJECT_NUMBER}/locations/{REGION}/pools/{POOL_UUID}/ontap/api/{ONTAP_RESOURCE}
```

### ONTAP API Resources
- `/storage/volumes` - Volume management (flexvol, flexgroup, dp types)
- `/storage/aggregates` - Aggregate management
- `/svm/svms` - SVM operations
- `/snapmirror/relationships` - SnapMirror replication
- `/cluster/jobs` - Job monitoring
- `/protocols/nfs`, `/protocols/cifs` - Protocol configurations

