## Key Differences: CCFE vs Proxy Endpoints

**GCP Project Identifiers:**
- **Project Name**: Human-readable name (e.g., "My NetApp Project") - for reference only
- **Project ID**: String identifier used in URLs (e.g., "my-netapp-project-123")
- **Project Number**: Numeric identifier (e.g., "846223794136")

| Aspect | CCFE Endpoint | Proxy Endpoint |
|--------|---------------|----------------|
| **GCNV Base URL** | Production: `https://netapp.googleapis.com/v1`<br>Autopush: `https://autopush-netapp.sandbox.googleapis.com/v1`<br>Staging: `https://staging-netapp.sandbox.googleapis.com/v1` | `https://ncv.us-c1.autopush-tst.internal.npd.gnf.netapp.com/v1beta` |
| **ONTAP Base URL** | Production: `https://netapp.googleapis.com/v1beta1`<br>Autopush: `https://autopush-netapp.sandbox.googleapis.com/v1beta1`<br>Staging: `https://staging-netapp.sandbox.googleapis.com/v1beta1` | `https://ncv.us-c1.autopush-tst.internal.npd.gnf.netapp.com/v1beta` |
| **Project Identifier** | Project ID (string) | Project Number (numeric) |
| **Location** | Zone (e.g., `us-east4-a`) or Region | Region (e.g., `us-central1`) |
| **Pool Identifier** | Pool Name | Pool UUID |
| **Request Body (ONTAP)** | Wrapped in `"body": {}` | Direct payload |
| **Authentication** | `Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN` | `Authorization: $JWT_TOKEN` (no Bearer prefix) |
| **Token Source** | `gcloud auth print-access-token` | JWT from service account (see `tools/proxy-jwt-token.py`) |

