## Authentication

### CCFE Authentication
Uses Bearer token from gcloud:
```bash
TOKEN=$(gcloud auth print-access-token)
curl -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" ...
```

### Proxy Authentication
Uses JWT token generated from service account (no "Bearer" prefix):
```bash
# Generate JWT using .cursor/rules/tools/proxy-jwt-token.py
python tools/proxy-jwt-token.py -s /path/to/service-account.json -p PROJECT_NUMBER
curl -H "Authorization: $JWT_TOKEN" ...
```

**Audience URL**: `https://cloudvolumesgcp-api.netapp.com`

**Note**: JWT token is optional. If not provided, leave the Authorization header empty or skip it.

