## ONTAP Expert Mode Request Examples

### CCFE Endpoint — Create DP Volume
```bash
curl -X POST \
  'https://autopush-netapp.sandbox.googleapis.com/v1beta1/projects/{PROJECT_ID}/locations/{ZONE}/storagePools/{POOL_NAME}/ontap/api/storage/volumes?return_records=true' \
  -H 'Authorization: Bearer {TOKEN}' \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{
    "body": {
      "name": "{VOLUME_NAME}",
      "svm": { "name": "{SVM_NAME}" },
      "aggregates": [{ "name": "aggr1" }],
      "size": "100GB",
      "style": "flexvol",
      "type": "dp",
      "space": {
        "snapshot": { "reserve_percent": 5 }
      }
    }
  }'
```

### Proxy Endpoint — Create FlexGroup Volume
```bash
curl -X POST \
  'http://localhost:8088/v1beta/projects/{PROJECT_NUMBER}/locations/{REGION}/pools/{POOL_ID}/ontap/api/storage/volumes' \
  -H 'Authorization: {JWT_TOKEN}' \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{
    "name": "{VOLUME_NAME}",
    "svm": { "name": "{SVM_NAME}" },
    "aggregates": [
      { "name": "aggr1" },
      { "name": "aggr1" },
      { "name": "aggr1" }
    ],
    "style": "flexgroup",
    "size": "4005GB"
  }'
```

