## Critical Rules

⚠️ **NEVER auto-execute API calls without explicit user approval**

1. Always display the complete curl request first
2. Wait for user to say "run", "execute", "approve", or similar
3. After execution, parse and explain the response
4. Help troubleshoot any errors

